Assuming also section A.5 (appendix A), the estimator given in (7) has the desired limit properties: consistency with the optimal nonparametric rate of convergence and asymptotic normal distribution (see Orbe et al.2000,2005). These results are based on two assumptions. First, all matrices \documentclass{aastex} \usepackage{amsbsy} \usepackage{amsfonts} \usepackage{amssymb} \usepackage{bm} \usepackage{mathrsfs} \usepackage{pifont} \usepackage{stmaryrd} \usepackage{textcomp} \usepackage{portland,xspace} \usepackage{amsmath,amsxtra} \usepackage[OT2,OT1]{fontenc} 
