We recall that seasonal restrictions introduce cross‐restrictions between parameters at different time periods, which is why all coefficients are estimated together. Thus, each estimated coefficient is a function of the whole sample through the smoothing parameterhand the seasonal penalty parameters vector λ. Note that the coefficient estimation (8) needs to invert
